  "id": "019d286a-f2d7-7750-81b8-1616fbe1a4ac",
  "content": "### Task 6: Update init_flags default and post-create help text\n\n### Task 7: Manual smoke test\n\n**Step 1: Run status to verify CUDA shows up**\n\nRun: `cd /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace && .devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh status`\nExpected: output includes `cuda` row with `enabled=disabled` and `gpu=not detected` (or GPU info if a GPU is present)\n\n**Step 2: Verify enable/disable error handling (no GPU environment)**\n\nRun: `cd /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace && .devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh enable cuda 2>&1; echo \"exit: $?\"`\nExpected: error message about no NVIDIA GPU detected, exit code 1\n\n**Step 3: Verify disable is safe when never enabled**\n\nRun: `cd /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace && .devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh disable cuda`\nExpected: warning about CPU binary backup not found, flag set to disabled\n\n**Step 4: Verify help text**\n\nRun: `cd /root/corvia-project/corvia-workspace && .devcontainer/scripts/corvia-workspace.sh`\nExpected: usage text shows `{ollama|surrealdb|cuda}`",
